snippet.title: Tenderfoot Tactics Release Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
An open-world tactics RPG coming to PC, Mac, and Linux on October 21, 2020.

A party of goblins, granted magic by an ancient spirit, wanders the archipelago, fighting back the terrible Fog. 

Buy now! (Steam and itch.io): https://linktr.ee/tenderfoottactics
About Ice Water Games: https://linktr.ee/icewatergames

Badru
Michael Bell
Isa Hutchinson
Taylor Thomas
Zoe Vartanian
Madison Pathe
